Neck Road, east from East 12th Street, showing the serpentine turn of Neck Road into Sheepshead Bay Road before continuing eastward at Homecrest Ave. At the right, is the Voorhies Sheppard house, and at the left background, is No. 2275 Homecrest Ave.

April 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
